## Mac and cheese recipe

- Sauce
    - Roux 1:1:1 butter to flour to gelatin from the pork fat
    - 2 tbsp roux
    - 1 tbsp butter
    - 1 quart milk
    -  ~2 tbsp heavy cream
    - parmesan
    - gouda
    - gruyere
    - brie
- brocolli steamed in a pan and cut small
- oyster mushrooms sauteed in garlic and butter
- 10 servings noodles for 2 pans
- breadcrums on top
- baked at 425 for 35 mins
